The **@available** mechanism was added to the clang compiler for Objective C with Xcode 9. It is modelled on the Swift #available syntax .And it is unavailable in Xamarin.iOS . You can use the following code 
```
if (UIDevice.CurrentDevice.CheckSystemVersion(13,0))
{
    //...           
}
else
{
   //...
}
```

